<h1>Hey, I'm Marcel</h1>

<p class="text-muted">A software engineer and founder based in Spain.</p>

<p class="text-muted">I'm building <a href="https://bold.video" target="_blank">Bold Video</a>—video intelligence for coaching programs. We help coaches turn their video libraries into AI-powered implementation support so students actually succeed (and stick around). I also make <a href="https://pidro.online" target="_blank">Pidro</a>, a multiplayer card game for iOS and Android.</p>

<p class="text-muted">My stack is Elixir and TypeScript, though these days most of my coding happens through AI.</p>

<p class="text-muted">Outside of work, I'm usually with my two kids, out running, or reading. Originally from Germany, now happily settled in southern Spain.</p>

<p class="font-semibold">Nice to have you here.</p>

